 * HTTP Calls: Enables server requests from the client using custom services or
   built-in functionalities like HttpClient.

 * File Uploads: Allows users to upload files using input components.

 * Authentication & Authorization: Integrates with standard authentication
   protocols, such as OAuth.

 * SEO: Blazor supports server-side pre-rendering, which enhances Search Engine
   Optimization.


